%% 3.1.2 Overview (Dashboard) — sequence diagram (layered)
%% Order: Actor > UI > Controller > Service > Repository > Database
%% Note: BE hiện chưa có DashboardController; đây là mục tiêu kiến trúc / aggregate API.
%%       KPIs map nghiệp vụ: Students, Routes, Revenue (Orders/Payments), Attendance.

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Actor as Admin
    participant UI as UI (Dashboard page)
    participant Ctl as Controller (DashboardController)
    participant Svc as Service (DashboardService)
    participant Repo as Repository (IRepository T / aggregates)
    participant DB as Database (SQL Server)

    Actor->>UI: Open Dashboard / click Overview
    UI->>UI: Show skeleton loaders (headlines + chart + table)

    UI->>Ctl: GET overview (e.g. /api/Dashboard/overview) with Bearer token
    Note over UI,Ctl: Optional: If-None-Match / cache key — BR02

    Ctl->>Svc: GetOverviewAsync(filters, cacheKey)

    par Aggregate KPIs
        Svc->>Repo: Query totals (students count, active routes, revenue period, check-ins)
        Repo->>DB: SQL / EF aggregates
        DB-->>Repo: scalar / grouped rows
        Repo-->>Svc: KPI raw metrics
    and Chart series (7 days)
        Svc->>Repo: Query time-series (e.g. daily attendance or revenue)
        Repo->>DB: SQL range query
        DB-->>Repo: series points
        Repo-->>Svc: chart data
    and Latest transactions (5)
        Svc->>Repo: Query latest TransactionLog / Order rows
        Repo->>DB: SQL TOP 5 ordered by time
        DB-->>Repo: rows
        Repo-->>Svc: latest tx list
    end

    Svc->>Svc: Compute MoM % deltas, apply cache TTL (BR02)
    Svc-->>Ctl: DashboardOverviewDto (KPIs + deltas + series + latest 5)
    Ctl-->>UI: 200 JSON (+ cache headers if used)

    UI->>UI: Remove skeleton, render 4 cards + line chart + table
    UI-->>Actor: Interactive chart tooltips on hover

    Note over Actor,DB: On cache timeout or manual refresh, UI repeats fetch (BR02).
